---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Home"
  description="Gas lawn equipment is loud, polluting, and unnecessary. Join 2,847 neighbors reclaiming quiet mornings through local policy change."
>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="section bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-950 via-brand-900 to-brand-800 text-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 text-white/90 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-accent-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-accent-400"></span>
        </span>
        A grassroots movement growing by the minute
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
        Your Saturday Morning<br />
        <span class="text-accent-400">Shouldn't Sound Like</span><br />
        a Construction Site.
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-100 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Gas-powered mowers and leaf blowers produce 95 decibels of noise and as much pollution
        as driving 300 miles — in your own backyard. We're changing that, one neighborhood at a time.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <a href="/campaigns/new" class="btn-accent text-lg px-8 py-4 w-full sm:w-auto shadow-lg shadow-accent-500/25">
          Start a Campaign &mdash; It's Free
        </a>
        <a href="/why" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10 px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors text-lg w-full sm:w-auto">
          See the Evidence
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-4">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-accent-400">95 dB</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-brand-100 mt-1">Average gas mower noise &mdash; like a motorcycle at your window</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-accent-400">5%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-brand-100 mt-1">Of U.S. air pollution comes from lawn equipment (EPA)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-accent-400">1hr</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-brand-100 mt-1">Gas blower = 1,100 miles of car emissions (CARB)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- The Before & After -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">The Problem &amp; The Solution</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-6">
          Same Lawn.<br />Wildly Different Experience.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-earth-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          On the left: a gas mower that hits 95 decibels — loud enough to cause hearing damage
          in under an hour. On the right: an electric mower at 65 decibels — quiet enough to
          have a conversation while mowing. The technology exists. Your HOA just hasn't required it yet.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-100 rounded-xl p-4">
            <div class="text-red-700 font-bold text-lg">Gas</div>
            <div class="text-red-600 text-sm">95 dB · 300 miles of car pollution per hour · Hearing damage risk</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-100 rounded-xl p-4">
            <div class="text-green-700 font-bold text-lg">Electric</div>
            <div class="text-green-600 text-sm">65 dB · Zero emissions · Conversation-level volume</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
        <img src="/images/before-after-noise.jpg" alt="Gas vs electric lawn equipment noise comparison" class="w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- The Three Paths -->
<section class="section bg-earth-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">Your Role</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">
        Wherever You Are, There's a Way In
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-earth-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Five minutes or five hours a week — we built a path for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-earth-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-3">The Reader</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          You found us through the book, a news article, or a friend's post. You want to understand what's happening and why it matters. No account needed.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-earth-500 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">1.</span> Read the manifesto (5 min)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">2.</span> Sign a petition near you (2 min)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">3.</span> Share on social media (30 sec)</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/manifesto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm mt-6 hover:text-brand-800">
          Start Reading <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border-2 border-brand-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 bg-accent-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full shadow">Most Impact</div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-3">The Organizer</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          You want to change the rules where you live. You're ready to start a petition, gather signatures, measure noise, and present to your HOA or city council.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-earth-500 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">1.</span> Pick a template (2 min)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">2.</span> Write your story (10 min)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">3.</span> Share with your network (3 min)</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/campaigns/new" class="btn-primary w-full text-center mt-6">
          Start a Campaign
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-earth-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 18.657A8 8 0 016.343 7.343S7 9 9 10c0-2 .5-5 2.986-7C14 5 16.09 5.777 17.656 7.343A7.975 7.975 0 0120 13a7.975 7.975 0 01-2.343 5.657z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-3">The Supporter</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          You already switched to electric, or you just want to help. Sign petitions, leave testimonials, comment on campaigns, and cheer on your local organizers.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-earth-500 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">1.</span> Browse campaigns near you</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">2.</span> Sign &amp; share (1 min each)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-brand-500 font-bold">3.</span> Tell your quiet morning story</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/wall" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm mt-6 hover:text-brand-800">
          See the Wall <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Community Action -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl order-2 md:order-1">
        <img src="/images/community-meeting.jpg" alt="Neighbors at an HOA meeting presenting quiet lawn equipment data" class="w-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">How Change Happens</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-6">
          From Your Block<br />to the Ballot Box
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-earth-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Every neighborhood that changes its rules becomes proof that the next neighborhood can too.
          Here's the path:
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          {[
            { step: '01', title: 'Read & Learn', desc: 'Understand the issue. Read the manifesto, browse the ordinance library. See what 12 other communities have already done.' },
            { step: '02', title: 'Start or Join', desc: 'Find a campaign near you or launch your own. Pick a template, set a goal, and tell your story — takes 15 minutes.' },
            { step: '03', title: 'Measure & Document', desc: 'Rent a calibrated sound meter from us. Upload real noise data. Win arguments with evidence, not anecdotes.' },
            { step: '04', title: 'Show Up Prepared', desc: 'Walk into your HOA meeting or city council with a speaker card, 3-minute remarks, and a signature list. We generate all of it for you.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold shrink-0">{item.step}</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-brand-900">{item.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-earth-500">{item.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Real Electric Mowing -->
<section class="section bg-brand-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">The Alternative Is Already Here</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">
        Electric Works. Here's Proof.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-earth-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Battery-powered mowers have reached performance parity with gas — for a fraction of the noise and zero emissions.
        Hundreds of thousands of homeowners have already switched.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <img src="/images/electric-mower-action.jpg" alt="Person mowing with a quiet electric mower on a sunny morning" class="w-full" />
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      {[
        { icon: '🔋', title: '45-90 min runtime', desc: 'Enough for most residential lawns on a single charge. Second batteries available for larger yards.' },
        { icon: '💰', title: 'Lower lifetime cost', desc: 'No gas, no oil, no spark plugs, no winterizing. Save $200+/year in operating costs.' },
        { icon: '🔇', title: 'Conversation-level noise', desc: 'Mow at 7 AM on Saturday. Your neighbors won\'t hear it — and they\'ll thank you.' },
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">{item.icon}</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-earth-500">{item.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a href="/measure/buy" class="btn-secondary">See Recommended Equipment</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Featured Testimonials -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-12">
      <div>
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Real Stories</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900">
          First Quiet Mornings
        </h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/wall" class="text-brand-600 font-semibold hover:text-brand-800 hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-1">
        See All Stories <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {[
        { quote: "I switched to electric and my neighbors thanked me. Now three other houses on my street have switched too.", author: "Mike R.", city: "Austin, TX", brand: "EGO" },
        { quote: "Never thought I'd care about lawn equipment. Then I had a baby who napped at 10 AM, and suddenly 7 AM leaf blowers weren't just annoying — they were ruining our lives.", author: "Jennifer L.", city: "Portland, OR", brand: "Greenworks" },
        { quote: "Got my entire block to go electric. We have a group chat now. Saturday mornings are actually peaceful. I forgot what birds sounded like.", author: "David C.", city: "Denver, CO", brand: "Milwaukee" },
      ].map(t => (
        <div class="bg-earth-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="text-earth-700 italic mb-4 leading-relaxed text-sm">&ldquo;{t.quote}&rdquo;</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-700 font-bold text-xs">
              {t.author.split(' ').map(n => n[0]).join('')}
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-earth-900 text-sm">{t.author}</div>
              <div class="text-earth-500 text-xs">{t.city} &middot; Switched to {t.brand}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-8 sm:hidden">
      <a href="/wall" class="btn-secondary">See All Stories</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Final CTA -->
<section class="section bg-brand-950 text-white">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
      Your Neighborhood Could Be Next.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-brand-200 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      It takes 15 minutes to start a campaign. Every signature moves the needle.
      Every HOA that changes its rules becomes proof that yours can too.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/campaigns/new" class="btn-accent text-lg px-8 py-4 shadow-lg shadow-accent-500/25">
        Start a Campaign
      </a>
      <a href="/wall/submit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10 px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors text-lg">
        Share Your Story
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm mt-8">No account required to sign a petition. Join 2,847 neighbors already taking action.</p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
